-X` change in `LineReaderImplTest`.\\\\n2. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.jline:jline-reader:4.0.0` and `./gradlew nativeTest -Pcoordinates=org.jline:jline-reader:4.0.0` to confirm the fix outside the automation loop.\\\\n3. If native verification still fails, inspect metadata/resource registration for `META-INF/jline/providers/ffm` and `META-INF/jline/providers/jni`.\\\"}}\\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/2494-b1a8ca1b/stats/org.apache.activemq/activemq-broker/6.0.0/stats.json:36:        \\\"missed\\\" : 5599,\\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/stats/org.apache.activemq/activemq-broker/6.0.0/stats.json:36:        \\\"missed\\\" : 5599,\\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/718-b53ff6bf/stats/org.apache.activemq/activemq-broker/6.0.0/stats.json:36:        \\\"missed\\\" : 5599,\\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/718-b53ff6bf/stats/org.ow2.asm/asm/9.4/execution-metrics.json:31:    \\\"ending_commit\\\": \\\"3a0064c8297d56362888dd20755996700529a6f3\\\",\\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/5013-4a4b6fa1/stats/org.apache.activemq/activemq-broker/6.0.0/stats.json:36:        \\\"missed\\\" : 5599,\\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/5013-4a4b6fa1/stats/org.ow2.asm/asm/9.4/execution-metrics.json:31:    \\\"ending_commit\\\": \\\"3a0064c8297d56362888dd20755996700529a6f3\\\",\\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/source_context/com.querydsl/querydsl-core/5.0.0/main/extracted/com/querydsl/core/types/PathMetadata.java:30:    private static final long serialVersionUID = -1055994185028970065L;\\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/loc